表的代码预览负责

drop index Responsible_PK on Responsible;


alter table Responsible
drop foreign key FK_RESPONSI_RESPONSIB_EMPLOYEE;

alter table Responsible
drop foreign key FK_RESPONSI_RESPONSIB_CLIENT;

drop table if exists Responsible;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: Responsible */
/*==============================================================*/
create table Responsible
(
employee_id varchar(20) not null comment '',
client_id varchar(20) not null comment '',
res_type tinyint comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Responsible_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index Responsible_PK on Responsible
(
employee_id,
client_id
);

alter table Responsible add constraint FK_RESPONSI_RESPONSIB_EMPLOYEE foreign key (employee_id)
references employee (employee_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table Responsible add constraint FK_RESPONSI_RESPONSIB_CLIENT foreign key (client_id)
references client (client_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
